{"word":"ἐυχαριστέω","slug":"ἐυχαριστέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐυχαριστέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εὐχάριστος\">εὐχάριστος</a></el>] <b>give thanks,</b> except for <b><a href='B:520 16:4'>Ro 16:4</a></b> and<b> <a href='B:490 17:16'>Lk 17:16</a></b> (but <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vs.\">vs.</a> 18)<b>,</b> God is explicitly or implicitly the recipient of thanksgiving <b><a href='B:470 15:36'>Mt 15:36</a>; <a href='B:470 26:27'>26:27</a>; <a href='B:490 18:11'>Lk 18:11</a>; <a href='B:500 11:41'>J 11:41</a>; <a href='B:520 1:8'>Ro 1:8</a>; <a href='B:530 1:14'>1 Cor 1:14</a>; <a href='B:560 1:16'>Eph 1:16</a>; <a href='B:590 5:18'>1 Th 5:18</a>; <a href='B:600 1:3'>2 Th 1:3</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 4</a>; <a href='B:730 11:17'>Rv 11:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐφροσύνη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐχαριστία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}